OL,3,CWaitrose to create 550 jobs for new
OL,4,CBristol warehouse as it eyes expansion
OL,6,FWaitrose is planning to hire around
OL,7,F550 staff to work at its new warehouse
OL,8,Fin Bristol as the upmarket grocer eyes
OL,9,Fexpansion in the region.
OL,11,FThe distribution centre will open in
OL,12,Fearly 2027 and be run by logistics
OL,13,Ffirm DHL, which is set to begin
OL,14,Frecruiting in spring.
OL,16,FSome 480 warehouse staff and 80
OL,17,Fdrivers will be brought in ahead of
OL,18,Fthe launch of the site in Avonmouth,
OL,19,FBristol.
