OL,3,CWaitrose to create 550 jobs for new
OL,4,CBristol warehouse as it eyes expansion
OL,6,FWaitrose said the new site will make
OL,7,Fdeliveries more efficient for the 50
OL,8,Fexisting shops in the south-west
OL,9,FEngland region, and pave the way for
OL,10,Fexpansion in the future.
OL,12,FIt is also hailed as the retailer's
OL,13,Fmost sustainable warehouse building,
OL,14,Fwith features including 1,200 solar
OL,15,Fpanels on the roof and energy
OL,16,Fefficient systems.
