OL,3,CWaitrose to create 550 jobs for new
OL,4,CBristol warehouse as it eyes expansion
OL,6,FThe retailer has committed to
OL,7,Finvesting #1 billion over several
OL,8,Fyears into growing the brand and
OL,9,Fimproving its 317 shops across the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FPart of this investment has involved
OL,13,Fspending on artificial intelligence
OL,14,F(AI) and automation, including to
OL,15,Freduce the number of manual processes
OL,16,Ffor work across the supply chain.
