OL,3,CWaitrose to create 550 jobs for new
OL,4,CBristol warehouse as it eyes expansion
OL,6,FIt has leaned into AI to identify what
OL,7,Finfluences customer behaviour and
OL,8,Ftheir spending patterns, such as
OL,9,Fsports events, weather changes, and
OL,10,Fpromotions.
OL,12,FWaitrose has been increasing its share
OL,13,Fof the UK grocery market and now
OL,14,Fcaptures 4.7% of the market, according
OL,15,Fto the latest figures from research
OL,16,Ffirm Worldpanel by Numerator.
