OL,3,CWaitrose to create 550 jobs for new
OL,4,CBristol warehouse as it eyes expansion
OL,6,FThe average amount spent by shoppers
OL,7,Fon a trip to the grocer increased by
OL,8,F6.5% over the 12 weeks to the end of
OL,9,FDecember 28, compared with the same
OL,10,Fperiod a year ago ` outpacing gains by
OL,11,Fits competitors.
OL,13,FThe brand, which is part of the John
OL,14,FLewis Partnership, will open its first
OL,15,Ffull-size supermarket for seven years
OL,16,Fin Brabazon, a new neighbourhood in
OL,17,Fnorth Bristol, next year.
OL,19,FIt has still expanded during the
OL,20,Fperiod, but through convenience and
OL,21,Fsmaller franchise stores.
